      <description>&lt;p&gt;In this blog series, we explore how to obfuscate a Metasploit payload to avoid detection by Antivirus Engines and shall try to go invisible.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We would employ known techniques and see how they affect detection rates uploading the compiled executable to &lt;a href=&#34;https://antiscan.me/&#34;&gt;AntiScan&lt;/a&gt; as it does not submit the samples to the vendors.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;admonition warning&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;admonition-header&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 512 512&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M256 32c14.2 0 27.3 7.5 34.5 19.8l216 368c7.3 12.4 7.3 27.7 .2 40.1S486.3 480 472 480L40 480c-14.3 0-27.6-7.7-34.7-20.1s-7-27.8 .2-40.1l216-368C228.7 39.5 241.8 32 256 32zm0 128c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24l0 112c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-112c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24zm32 224a32 32 0 1 0 -64 0 32 32 0 1 0 64 0z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;span&gt;Antiscan.me is no longer active so some links might be broken&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;environment-setup&#34;&gt;Environment Setup&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To begin with, we would be needing some tools and setup to get started. The first thing is the unobfuscated shellcode we&amp;rsquo;ll be using:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
